WEBVTT

00:07.873 --> 00:09.662
<i>Previously on </i> Cloak and Dagger...

00:09.687 --> 00:11.143
You mean, you see people's fears, too?

00:11.189 --> 00:13.385
<i>Ironically, I can see their hopes.</i>

00:13.432 --> 00:15.079
Yo, Billy. We found his car

00:15.080 --> 00:16.510
and we're gonna take back
our radio. You comin'?

00:16.572 --> 00:18.709
Nah, man. I'm gonna
stay with my brother.

00:18.710 --> 00:20.289
We're going to the
State Finals next week,

00:20.290 --> 00:22.210
and we're concerned that
you're gonna screw it up for us.

00:24.580 --> 00:26.580
What?

00:28.170 --> 00:30.628
I have a couple questions
to ask you about Roxxon.

00:30.670 --> 00:32.549
- Maybe help.
<i>- I've never turned down free help.</i>

00:32.573 --> 00:34.290
<i>They're leaving a big paper trail.</i>

00:36.000 --> 00:42.074
Learn the unknown English words
of this movie at www.skeebdo.com

00:53.727 --> 00:56.106
I joined the Navy to help people.

00:56.194 --> 00:59.153
When I lost my arm
building a hospital in Mosul,

00:59.178 --> 01:00.609
I thought that was it.

01:00.727 --> 01:03.266
Then, Roxxon Gulf approached me

01:03.337 --> 01:06.176
about applying my skills
to the city I called home.

01:06.240 --> 01:09.489
Who says nation building should
only be about other nations?

01:09.603 --> 01:11.522
My name is Louden Swift,

01:11.546 --> 01:13.043
<i>and I'm working with Roxxon Gulf</i>

01:13.068 --> 01:14.999
<i>to make the world a better place.</i>

