01:50.380 --> 01:53.213
<i>♪ Back and forth again and rewind ♪</i>

01:53.266 --> 01:56.510
<i>♪ Those thoughts, they can't be mine ♪</i>

01:56.606 --> 01:58.884
<i>♪ Wouldn't be yours if you tried ♪</i>

01:59.002 --> 02:01.540
<i>♪ So what do you want? ♪</i>

02:02.556 --> 02:04.620
<i>♪ Please tell me, tell me ♪</i>

02:04.710 --> 02:07.750
<i>♪ 'Cause I know what I want ♪</i>

